Title: ندورة حوارية بعنوان "المجلس المركزي الفلسطيني-مقدمات ونتائج"
AltTitle.other: A seminar entitled "The Palestinian Central Council - Introduction and Results"
Description.note: A colour photograph of Majida al-Masry, Ahmad Abdel-Rahman, Qais Abdel-Kareem "Abu Laila" and Hassan Yousef during a seminar held by the Democratic Front for the Liberation of Palestine entitled "The Palestinian Central Council - Introduction and Results" in 2003. Title: ماجدة المصري في بيت إكسا
AltTitle.other: Majida al-Masry in Beit Iksa
Description.note: Taken on 13 January 2013, this colour photograph shows Majida al-Masry, a politburo member of the Democratic Front for the Liberation of Palestine (DFLP), at a non-violent sit-in near Bait Iksa. This non-violent action ushered in a new non-violent resistance by setting up Bab Shams and Bab al-Karama tented villages in the face of the Israeli colonial plans between al-Quds (Jerusalem) and Ma'ale Adumim colony. |~|صورة ملونة التُقطت نهار 13 كانون الثاني عام 2013 تظهر فيها ماجدة المصري، عضو المكتب السياسي للجبهة الديمقراطية لتحرير فلسطين، تتحدث خلال تجمع بالقرب من بيت إكسا حيث بدأ ناشطون فلسطينيون شكلًا جديدًا من المقاومة بتشييد قريتي باب شمس وباب الكرامة من الخيام لمقاومة المخططات الاستعماريّة الإسرائيليّة بين القدس ومستعمرة معاليه أدوميم.
References: Majida al-Masri (Collection owner), interview with PMDA researcher Lama Ghosheh, October 2019, non-transcript, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.; Mahmoud Jiddah (Collection owner), interview with PMDA researcher Lama Ghosheh, February 2019, non-transcript, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.

Series & Collection: Majida al-Masri Sub-collection 1: Photographs | The Majida al-Masri Collection
Description (Eng): Taken on 13 January 2013, this colour photograph shows Majida al-Masry, a politburo member of the Democratic Front for the Liberation of Palestine (DFLP), at a non-violent sit-in near Bait Iksa.
